  3. Coach Page Can't Find Data: It's filtering by user_id, but yours is NULL, so it returns empty results

  Your Database Schema is Actually Perfect!

  The schema already has proper user_id columns and foreign keys to auth.users. It's ready for real authentication - you just need to implement
  Supabase Auth.

