  Option 1: Quick Fix (Testing Today)
  - Hardcode a demo user ID throughout the app
  - All your data gets linked to one fake user
  - Lets you test immediately but not secure

  Option 2: Proper Solution (Production Ready)
  - Implement real Supabase Authentication
  - Add signup/login with email/password
  - Each athlete gets their own account
  - Data is properly protected

  My Recommendation

